        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="green" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">A me</span><span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="true" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>non<span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="false" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>interessano<span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="true" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>i<span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="false" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>pettegolezzi.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="green" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">A chi</span><span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="true" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>avete<span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="false" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>lasciato<span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="true" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>il<span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="false" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>vostro<span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="false" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>gatto?</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2 -->
  <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 pb-8">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
      Indica con una X se il complemento evidenziato è un complemento oggetto (O) o un complemento di termine (T).
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between gap-3">
          <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Porterò <strong>a Rimini</strong> la nonna.</span>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
              <input type="radio" name="ex2_1" value="O" class="w-4 h-4">
              <span class="font-semibold">O</span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
              <input type="radio" name="ex2_1" value="T" class="w-4 h-4">
              <span class="font-semibold">T</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
